"""
# JS → Simple API Capability Matrix

Comparison of JavaScript Web APIs and their Simple browser engine equivalents.
Each row maps a JS API to the corresponding Simple module and function.

## DOM API (dom_api.spl)
| JS API                          | Simple Function                  | Status    |
|----------------------------------|----------------------------------|-----------|
| document.querySelector()         | document_query_selector()        | Done      |
| document.querySelectorAll()      | document_query_selector_all()    | Done      |
| document.getElementById()        | document_get_element_by_id()     | Done      |
| document.createElement()         | document_create_element()        | Done      |
| document.createTextNode()        | document_create_text_node()      | Done      |
| node.appendChild()               | node_append_child()              | Done      |
| node.removeChild()               | node_remove_child()              | Done      |
| node.insertBefore()              | node_insert_before()             | Done      |
| node.setAttribute()              | node_set_attribute()             | Done      |
| node.getAttribute()              | node_get_attribute()             | Done      |
| node.removeAttribute()           | node_remove_attribute()          | Done      |
| node.textContent = x             | node_set_text_content()          | Done      |
| node.textContent                 | node_get_text_content()          | Done      |
| node.innerHTML = x               | node_set_inner_html()            | Partial   |
| node.classList.add()             | node_class_list_add()            | Done      |
| node.classList.remove()          | node_class_list_remove()         | Done      |
| node.classList.toggle()          | node_class_list_toggle()         | Done      |
| node.classList.contains()        | node_class_list_contains()       | Done      |
| node.style.setProperty()         | node_set_style_property()        | Done      |
| node.style.getPropertyValue()    | node_get_style_property()        | Partial   |
| node.parentNode                  | node_parent()                    | Stub      |
| node.children                    | node_children()                  | Done      |
| node.tagName                     | node_tag_name()                  | Done      |

