## Location / History API (location_api.spl)
| JS API                          | Simple Function                  | Status    |
|----------------------------------|----------------------------------|-----------|
| window.location                  | BrowserLocation                  | Done      |
| location.assign()                | location_assign()                | Done      |
| location.reload()                | location_reload()                | No-op     |
| location.href / protocol / etc.  | BrowserLocation fields           | Done      |
| history.pushState()              | history_push_state()             | Done      |
| history.replaceState()           | history_replace_state()          | Done      |
| history.back()                   | history_back()                   | Done      |
| history.forward()                | history_forward()                | Done      |
| history.go()                     | history_go()                     | Done      |

## Status Legend
- Done    = fully implemented
- Partial = works for common cases, not all edge cases
- Stub    = API surface defined, body is pass_todo or returns dummy data
- Model   = in-memory model, no real I/O
- Approx  = approximate/estimated result
- No-op   = intentionally does nothing in the in-memory model
